23:55.983 --> 24:11.669
answering questions for the astronauts. I 
remember writing a little paper for Jocelyn on...

24:16.529 --> 24:31.145
meteors as a little information paper for the to go 
to the then Mercury and I guess by then Gemini

24:16.529 --> 24:31.145
astronauts.

