and I'd always kind of expressed interest in the 
lunar program I was referred to a

24:44.170 --> 24:52.543
conference that was being held in Chicago. At 
O'Hare Airport. At O'Hare Airport. And I was the

24:54.366 --> 24:56.329
guy that arranged it and chaired it. Right. It was 
on the military orbiting laboratory. And at this

24:59.654 --> 25:11.292
time, there were discussions about merging the 
Air Force Orbiting Laboratory Program and NASA's

24:59.654 --> 25:11.292
plans for orbiting laboratories. And this was 
called the MOL conference or something. And I

