Live Space Telescope, got to be 120 inches because 
Aidan Meinel was there. And I asked him, what's the

25:31.596 --> 25:35.060
biggest diffraction thing we could have in 10 
years? And he said 120 inches. It was at that

25:36.381 --> 25:41.427
meeting that I came in knowing very little about 
what was going on. I, of course, had heard of the Air

25:41.568 --> 25:44.451
Force program And I knew there were general 
long-range plans on the part of NASA. And it

